title: I got an S+ and didnt get a mast level 7 token.

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
Can i please have my token. It was 4v5 and i had to try hard to win :( 

I should have gotten it but didnt for some reason.

replies.body:
Hey there,

[This is probably related to the known issue that occasionally causes mastery tokens not to drop, this should be resolved in an upcoming patch.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/208872326--May-20-We-re-aware-of-an-issue-that-occasionally-prevents-mastery-token-drops-We-re-aiming-to-resolve-this-in-patch-6-11)
